OL,3,CInquest begins into couple who were
OL,4,Ckilled in crash near Appleby
OL,6,FAn inquest has heard how a young
OL,7,Fcouple were found dead inside a
OL,8,Fcrashed van hours after it was
OL,9,Ffollowed by a police officer on mobile
OL,10,Fpatrol.
OL,12,FEllie Marsden, 20, and 24-year-old
OL,13,FRyan Duffy, had travelled from their
OL,14,FGreater Manchester homes to spend a
OL,15,Fnight at Appleby-in-Westmorland, on
OL,16,FSaturday 4 September 2021.
