OL,6,FThey arrived and were checked in at
OL,7,Faround 10pm by duty manager James
OL,8,FUsher. "The man (Ryan) said something
OL,9,Falong the lines of 'I just want to
OL,10,Fmake her happy with a night away',"
OL,11,Fsaid Mr Usher in a statement read to
OL,12,Fthe inquest in Carlisle. "Both were
OL,13,Ffriendly. They seemed in good spirits."
OL,15,FEllie and Ryan went to a pub, where
OL,16,Fthey remained until just after 12:30am.
