OL,4,Ckilled in crash near Appleby
OL,6,FA police officer on mobile patrol in a
OL,7,Fmarked Ford Transit, close to the town
OL,8,Fcentre pub, saw Ellie, of Golborne,
OL,9,Fgetting into the passenger seat of a
OL,10,Fwhite Citroen Berlingo van, which was
OL,11,Fthen driven away by Ryan, from Ashton-
OL,12,Fin-Makerfield.
OL,14,FThat constable decided to follow the
OL,15,Fvan, which was seen to travel the
OL,16,Fwrong way along a one-way street. It
OL,17,Fthen turned right on to Boroughgate.
