OL,6,F"The officer followed the van on to
OL,7,Frural roads around Appleby," assistant
OL,8,Fcoroner Joseph Hart told an 11-strong
OL,9,Fjury as he resumed an inquest into the
OL,10,Fdeaths of Ellie and Ryan today.
OL,12,F"At times he seems to have lost sight
OL,13,Fof the van. You will hear about how
OL,14,Fthe officer followed that vehicle on
OL,15,Fthose rural roads. But at this stage
OL,16,Fyou should be aware the officer didn't
OL,17,Filluminate his emergency blue lights.
