OL,6,F"After a distance the officer ceased
OL,7,Fto follow that vehicle, and he thought
OL,8,Fthe driver might in fact have been
OL,9,Faware of his presence."
OL,11,FThe officer notified police force
OL,12,Fcontrol of his observations regarding
OL,13,Fthe Citroen van. He returned to
OL,14,FAppleby and later pulled over a
OL,15,Fsimilar van in the town centre which
OL,16,Fproved not to be the Citroen he had
OL,17,Foriginally spotted,
