OL,6,FHours later, at around 7:40am, a
OL,7,Fmarried couple travelling along the
OL,8,Fnarrow single carriageway C3057 road `
OL,9,Faround three miles south-east of the
OL,10,Fvillage of Kings Meaburn ` came across
OL,11,Fa crashed van. Inside were the bodies
OL,12,Fof Ellie and Ryan.
OL,14,F"The van was straight off the road and
OL,15,Fhad crashed into a big tree," stated
OL,16,Fwitness Bill Offord, who had been
OL,17,Ftravelling with his wife.
