OL,6,FThere were skid marks on the road and
OL,7,Fextensive damage to the Berlingo. "The
OL,8,Ffront of the vehicle was destroyed. It
OL,9,Fmust have been a huge impact with the
OL,10,Ftree," Mr Offord also stated.
OL,12,FBefore evidence began, assistant
OL,13,Fcoroner Mr Hart told jurors they would
OL,14,Fhave to consider a number of issues
OL,15,Fduring what was a "fact-finding"
OL,16,Fhearing to establish facts but not to
OL,17,Fapportion blame.
