OL,6,FJurors would consider the route and
OL,7,Fjourney taken by Ryan. "You will
OL,8,Fconsider the corresponding movements
OL,9,Fand the speed of the police officer
OL,10,Fwhen he was following the van," said
OL,11,FMr Hart. "You will have to consider
OL,12,Fwhether the police officer was
OL,13,Finvolved in pursuing the Duffy van.
OL,14,FYou will have to consider the
OL,15,Fofficer's decision to stop following
OL,16,Fthat van."
