OL,6,FKaren Duffy said of Ryan, who loved
OL,7,Fnature, camping, cycling, climbing,
OL,8,Fwalking and angling: "He was a larger
OL,9,Fthan life character, always smiling
OL,10,Fand happy. He could light up a room
OL,11,Fwith his infectious laugh.
OL,13,F"He was fearless and would have a go
OL,14,Fat anything. Ryan's philosophy for
OL,15,Flife was to grab it by the horns and
OL,16,Flive it to the full. He made me proud
OL,17,Fevery day."
