OL,6,FEllie, said Ryan's mum, was very
OL,7,Fspecial in his life with "two
OL,8,Fbeautiful souls having been "taken too
OL,9,Fsoon".
OL,11,F"I do know that the world is a poorer
OL,12,Fplace for Ryan and Ellie not being in
OL,13,Fit.," she said. "He was my world and
OL,14,Fwill be missed always."
OL,16,FKelly Kennedy paid tribute to Ellie,
OL,17,Fdaughter of Allan and sister of Chloe.
