OL,6,F"Ellie always wore her heart on her
OL,7,Fsleeve and had the most impeccable
OL,8,Fmanners with a genuine kindness and
OL,9,Flove radiating from her," said her mum.
OL,11,FEllie was "loyal, loving, caring, kind
OL,12,Fand genuine", loved make-up, fashion
OL,13,Fand ice cream.
OL,15,F"So many hearts have been broken by
OL,16,FEllie's loss. So many," said her mum,
OL,17,Fwho called her "indescribably special".
